title: Creating Phantom Enemies - The Weird Way Genshin Impact Loads Stuff

media:group.media:title: Creating Phantom Enemies - The Weird Way Genshin Impact Loads Stuff
media:group.media:description:
Genshin Impact has a weird way of loading things. Instead of draw distance, they have load zones. When enemies cross these zones, it can lead to some odd behavior...

Interested in more odd mechanics? Here's how to switch your character's default expression, even outside of Photo Mode: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ElfWGdMO33g

Follow on Twitter for sneak peeks and strange finds: https://twitter.com/Moosashiden
